<subSubSection id="C34F8499FFAF9364FF25F8EBFD81F83A" pageId="7" pageNumber="540" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BEAD712FFAF9364FF25F8EBFD81F83A" blockId="7.[151,1437,716,2039]" pageId="7" pageNumber="540">
<emphasis id="B9210B00FFAF9364FF25F8EBFEF8F847" bold="true" box="[199,315,1904,1930]" pageId="7" pageNumber="540">Remarks.</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFC4AAE3FFAF9364FEA1F8EBFDCFF846" author="Kirejtshuk, A. G." box="[323,524,1904,1931]" pageId="7" pageNumber="540" pagination="44 - 82" refId="ref10996" refString="Kirejtshuk, A. G. (1986) Revision of the genus Aethina Er. (Coleoptera, Nitidulidae) of the fauna of the Oriental and Palaearctic regions. Trudy Zoologischeskogo Instituta AN SSSR, 140, 44 - 82. [in Russian]" type="journal article" year="1986">Kirejtshuk (1986)</bibRefCitation>
while revising 
<taxonomicName id="4C55AC91FFAF9364FD5FF8EBFCD7F847" authorityName="Erichson" authorityYear="1843" box="[701,788,1904,1930]" class="Insecta" family="Nitidulidae" genus="Aethina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="540" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B9210B00FFAF9364FD5FF8EBFCD7F847" box="[701,788,1904,1930]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="540">Aethina</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
of Oriental and Palaearctic regions, synonymised 
<taxonomicName id="4C55AC91FFAF9364FAB3F8EBFE32F863" authority="Grouvelle, 1903" authorityName="Grouvelle" authorityYear="1903" class="Insecta" family="Nitidulidae" genus="Aethina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="540" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="nigrocastanea" subGenus="Aethina">
<emphasis id="B9210B00FFAF9364FAB3F8EBFEF5F863" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="540">A. (A.) nigrocastanea</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFC4AAE3FFAF9364FEDEF80FFE32F863" author="Grouvelle, A." box="[316,497,1940,1966]" pageId="7" pageNumber="540" pagination="108 - 124" refId="ref10668" refString="Grouvelle, A. (1903) Clavicornes de l'Inde septentrionale recoltes par M. Harmand. Nitidulidae. - Colydiidae. - Cucujidae. - Monotomidae. - Dryopidae. Annales de la Societe Entomologique de France, 72, 108 - 124." type="journal article" year="1903">Grouvelle, 1903</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
with 
<taxonomicName id="4C55AC91FFAF9364FDCDF80FFD02F863" authorityName=": Kirejtshuk" authorityYear="1986" box="[559,705,1940,1966]" class="Insecta" family="Nitidulidae" genus="Aethina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="540" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vicina" subGenus="Aethina">
<emphasis id="B9210B00FFAF9364FDCDF80FFD02F863" box="[559,705,1940,1966]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="540">A. (A.) vicina</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. The re-description of the species 
<taxonomicName id="4C55AC91FFAF9364FBDFF80FFB0CF863" authorityName=": Kirejtshuk" authorityYear="1986" box="[1085,1231,1940,1966]" class="Insecta" family="Nitidulidae" genus="Aethina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="540" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vicina" subGenus="Aethina">
<emphasis id="B9210B00FFAF9364FBDFF80FFB0CF863" box="[1085,1231,1940,1966]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="540">A. (A.) vicina</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is based primarily on 
<specimenCount id="9D531C9BFFAF9364FF58F822FEF6F81F" box="[186,309,1976,2003]" pageId="7" pageNumber="540" type="female">one female</specimenCount>
specimen from 
<collectingRegion id="499119F0FFAF9364FE08F823FDAAF81F" box="[490,617,1976,2002]" country="India" name="Meghalaya" pageId="7" pageNumber="540">Meghalaya</collectingRegion>
, determined by A. Grouvelle, in the ZSI; the illustration of male genitalia by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFC4AAE3FFAF9364FF58F847FE41F83A" author="Kirejtshuk, A. G." box="[186,386,2012,2039]" pageId="7" pageNumber="540" pagination="44 - 82" refId="ref10996" refString="Kirejtshuk, A. G. (1986) Revision of the genus Aethina Er. (Coleoptera, Nitidulidae) of the fauna of the Oriental and Palaearctic regions. Trudy Zoologischeskogo Instituta AN SSSR, 140, 44 - 82. [in Russian]" type="journal article" year="1986">Kirejtshuk (1986)</bibRefCitation>
was relied upon.
</paragraph>
